---
layout: base.njk
title: Shot Okay Films — Film & Photography Production in Coimbatore
permalink: /
---
{% from "icons.njk" import serviceIcon %}

<div class="hero-outer">
  <div class="pgm-monitor">
    <div class="pgm-top">
      <span class="tally-dot on"></span>
      <span class="mono">PGM · LIVE</span>
      <span class="tc mono">00:00:00:00</span>
    </div>

    <div class="pgm-screen">
      <h1>
        Every idea starts with a vision.<br>
        We work until the frame says, <span class="accent">“Shot Okay.”</span>
      </h1>

      <p class="subhead">
        Creative film and photography production from Coimbatore, built for brands, people, products, and stories that deserve attention.
      </p>

      <div class="cta-row">
        <a href="/contact/" class="btn-rec">Get a Free Quote</a>
        <a href="https://wa.me/{{ site.whatsapp }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="tel-link">
          or WhatsApp us directly →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="waveform" id="waveform"></div>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="wall-section">
  <div class="wrap">
    <span class="eyebrow mono">VIDEO VILLAGE — MONITOR WALL</span>
    <h2>What we shoot</h2>

    <div class="wall-grid">
      {% for s in services.services %}
      <div
        class="monitor{% if loop.first %} active{% endif %}"
        data-id="{{ s.id }}"
        data-headline="{{ s.headline }}"
        data-desc="{{ s.description }}"
      >
        <div class="mtop">
          <span class="tally-dot{% if loop.first %} on{% endif %}"></span>
          <span class="mono">{{ s.cam }}</span>
          <span class="tc mono">00:00:00:00</span>
        </div>

        <div class="mscreen">
          {{ serviceIcon(s.icon) }}
          <span class="sname">{{ s.name }}</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>

    <div class="wall-panel">
      <h3>{{ services.services[0].headline }}</h3>
      <p>{{ services.services[0].description }}</p>

      <a
        href="/contact/?service={{ services.services[0].name | urlencode }}"
        class="btn-rec"
      >
        Quote this shoot
      </a>
    </div>

    <a href="/services/" class="view-all-link">→ View all services</a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="wall-section">
  <div class="wrap">
    <span class="eyebrow mono">SELECTED WORK</span>
    <h2>Featured projects</h2>

    <div class="portfolio-grid">
      {% for project in collections.projects | reverse %}
        {% if project.data.featured %}

        <div class="pf-card">
          <div class="pf-screen">
            <span class="pf-label mono">REEL</span>
          </div>

          <div class="pf-meta">
            <span class="pf-name">{{ project.data.title }}</span>
            <span class="pf-tag mono">{{ project.data.category }}</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        {% endif %}
      {% else %}

        <div class="pf-card">
          <div class="pf-screen">
            <span class="pf-label mono">REEL 01</span>
          </div>
          <div class="pf-meta">
            <span class="pf-name">Commercials & Brand Films</span>
            <span class="pf-tag mono">Coming soon</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="pf-card">
          <div class="pf-screen">
            <span class="pf-label mono">REEL 02</span>
          </div>
          <div class="pf-meta">
            <span class="pf-name">Product Photo & Video</span>
            <span class="pf-tag mono">Coming soon</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="pf-card">
          <div class="pf-screen">
            <span class="pf-label mono">REEL 03</span>
          </div>
          <div class="pf-meta">
            <span class="pf-name">Films & Original Content</span>
            <span class="pf-tag mono">Coming soon</span>
          </div>
        </div>

      {% endfor %}
    </div>

    <a href="/portfolio/" class="view-all-link">→ View full portfolio</a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="notes-section">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="notes-grid">

      <div class="note">
        <span class="mono">CREW NOTE 01</span>
        <h3>One team, every frame</h3>
        <p>
          From commercials and product campaigns to spaces and original films —
          one creative team, one consistent visual language.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="note">
        <span class="mono">CREW NOTE 02</span>
        <h3>Shot for the platform</h3>
        <p>
          Every frame is composed for where people actually watch it —
          from the big screen to the smallest scroll.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="note">
        <span class="mono">CREW NOTE 03</span>
        <h3>Direction, not just a camera</h3>
        <p>
          Concept, lighting, movement, and story come built in —
          because a good-looking frame should still have something to say.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-banner">
  <div class="wrap">
    <h2>Have an idea worth shooting?</h2>

    <div class="cta-row">
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn-rec">Let's make it Shot Okay</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
